4. reserve() vs resize()
-------------------------

reserve(n)
-----------
- Changes capacity only.
- Does NOT create elements.
- Size remains unchanged.

Example:
v.reserve(100);

resize(n)
----------
- Changes size.
- Creates/removes elements.
- Capacity may increase.

Example:
v.resize(100);

